nodes.text: Carina was a Twi'lek female who worked for the Galactic Republic's Republic Strategic Information Service during the Cold War.

While she was stationed on the planet Nar Shaddaa, her astromech droid named TC-93 went rogue and fled to Network Security District with top secret SIS intel. She tasked a Republic spacer to wipe out the droid's memory and bring a copy of the data. In order to succeed, she gave the spacer a scanner to use on the renegade security droids in the district.
